{
  "id": "adv_main_01_06_02",
  "title": "星見編2章17話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_lesson-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……これが、私達の新曲",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So this is our new song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "どうだ？\nなかなかいい曲があがってきたと思うんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you think?\nI think it’s a pretty good song‚ personally.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.853197240829468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "はい\n凄くいいと思います……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes.\nI think it’s very good!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.663539085388184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣も好きだな、この曲\nステージで歌うのが楽しみだな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I like this song‚ too.\nI can’t wait to sing it on stage!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.34820868174235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "曲も出来たことですし……センターポジションや\nそれぞれのパートを決めないといけないですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that the song is finished‚ we’ll need to decide\nwho has the center position and all the other parts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.04820868174235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……それだけど、考えていることがある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About that‚ I have some thoughts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.948208681742347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "聞かせてください",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ tell us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.14820868174235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "激戦になるであろう、グランプリのことを考えると――\n一番大切なのは“インパクト”",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I think about how the Grand Prix is probably going to be a heated competition‚\nI think the most essential quality for a team is its impact.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.41560097932816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それも『月のテンペスト』であることを\n最大限に主張することが重要だと思ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s important to show everyone who Moon Tempest is‚\nand advocate for and promote yourselves to the max.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.93611379984098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "どういうこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.926930043330565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "月ストならではの特徴を出そう\nということですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you saying we should emphasize the features\nthat make Moon Tempest unique?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.37693006717242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "なら、やっぱり琴乃ちゃんがセンターをやるのが\n月ストにとって一番じゃないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ making Kotono our center\nwould be the best move for Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.376930067172424,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "んー？\nそういう話じゃないんじゃないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm?\nI don’t think that’s what he means.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.6947274943069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-cmn001.m4a",
      "text": "え……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.794727494306905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、だからさ、月ストには琴乃ちゃんがいるけど\n琴乃ちゃんだけが月ストじゃないでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like‚ what I mean is‚ yes‚ Kotono is in Moon Tempest‚\nbut there’s more to Moon Tempest than just Kotono‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.394727494306935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "んんん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.2725053886449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "だからー琴乃ちゃんがいても\nすずにゃんがいなかったら、月ストじゃないでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I mean‚ even if Kotono is in the group‚\nwe just wouldn’t be Moon Tempest without Suzu-nyan‚ would we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.93917205531156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 71.7725053886449
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "つまり……琴乃ちゃんがいて、渚ちゃんがいて\nすずちゃんがいて、芽衣ちゃんがいて、私がいる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In other words… Kotono is here‚ Nagisa is here‚\nSuzu is here‚ Mei is here‚ and I’m also here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.43917205531154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう！\nこの五人が揃って月スト！　みたいな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right!\nIt’s like‚ the five of us equals Moon Tempest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.37250538864488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "うん……分かる\n誰が欠けても月ストじゃないってことよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… I understand.\nYou’re saying Moon Tempest wouldn’t be Moon Tempest without all of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.63917205531156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "「月のテンペストであることを最大限に主張する」って\nそういうことかなって。違う？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I think “advocating for and promoting ourselves to the max”\nprobably means something like that. Am I wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.77250538864492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "私もそう思う\n全員のアピールパートを作るのはどう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I agree with you.\nHow about we all figure out our “strengths” in the group?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.43917212378052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "アピールパート！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our strengths?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.80583879044718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "少なくとも、それぞれの個性を表現するパートが\n欲しいと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At the very least‚ I think each one of us should have a way\nof expressing what makes us unique.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.91425154100928,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "……メンバーの自己紹介代わり\nというわけですわね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Instead of simply introducing ourselves individually…\nis that what you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7380610648188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん、いいね\nそれ分かりやすい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I like it!\nIt makes total sense!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.80472773148549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "何他人事のように見てるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you just watching them like an outsider?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "メンバー同士で答えを出してくれるなら\n俺が口を挟む必要はないと思ってさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As long as they’re finding their own answers as a team‚\nthere’s no need for me to insert myself into the conversation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.20472782685287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "それはそうかもね。でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You may be right. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.99270426010196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "渚もそれでいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you cool with that‚ Nagisa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.10299907898013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　う、うん\nもちろんだよ、琴乃ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Y-yeah.\nOf course I am‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.6276022630444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
